## Level 1 Specification

Grade: 1  
World: Sensing  
Big Idea: Machines sense the world using inputs, not understanding.

### Assets
- Story (multi-format, multi-language)
- Concept video
- HTML interactive game
- Worksheets (PDF)
- Teacher guide

Level 1 Completion Logic:

Digital Explorer Badge:
- Story viewed
- Video viewed
- Game participated

Sense Maker Badge:
- Discussion conducted
- Unplugged activity completed
- Facilitator confirmation

